This is water that has been blessed by a priest, and collected in vials. Whilst seemingly no different to standard water, when thrown at unholy creatures (undead and demonic), it will burn into their flesh, causing them great pain.

Note that whilst not strictly a magical weapon, in that its power derives from divine power rather than magic, this will harm unholy creatures that are normally only affected by magical weapons.
</weapon>

